column1: Unless otherwise noted, for any field that is cleaned the cleaning process includes:
1) If text is present in a numeric field translate text to numbers as possible.
3) If a numerical range is present the midpoint is calculated.
4) For year fields, the earliest year present is selected.
5) For currency fields, currency are cleaned to remove excess zeros.
6) When necessary for programs that use non-USD currencies, financials are converted to USD using the mid year exchange rate of the application year.
For fields that contain labeled data
1) For fields containing labeled data the text is standardized and converted to the appropriate label value
The availability of selection information (selected, showup, and finished) is subject to the program structure and timing of the program partners.
This release contains the most up-to-date selection information from the partners.
